nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE POISED TO BECOME A HURRICANE LATER TODAY...
summary: ...GABRIELLE POISED TO BECOME A HURRICANE LATER TODAY... As of 11:00 AM AST Sun Sep 21 the center of Gabrielle was located near 27.7, -61.0 with movement NW at 12 mph. The minimum central pressure was 995 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
